= pep =
pep is an utility to :
 * read
 * search
 * maintain an updated local version
of Python Enhancement Proposals from command line :

 * pep 8 // To read the PEP 8
 * pep search guido // To search guido
 * pep upgrade // To update local version of PEPs
 * pep upgrade with progress // To update local version showing a progression

Use the `pep upgrade with progress` the first time !

